medical result of my son?

218
00:18:09,021 --> 00:18:12,252
Mrs Luk, we don't want
to hide it from you.

219
00:18:14,793 --> 00:18:16,727
Luk Fai's disease is a
serious non-lymphatic cell

220
00:18:16,895 --> 00:18:18,829
Type M4 haemophilia

221
00:18:19,598 --> 00:18:20,587
which is blood cancer.

222
00:18:22,935 --> 00:18:24,061
In a simple terms,

223
00:18:24,503 --> 00:18:26,801
it's a abnormal change of the
white blood cells in his blood.

224
00:18:27,706 --> 00:18:30,573
And this abnormal
cells continue to grow,

225
00:18:30,742 --> 00:18:31,709
at a great rate.

226
00:18:32,010 --> 00:18:34,501
If it didn't cure in time,
the death rate is very high.

227
00:18:35,047 --> 00:18:36,514
So, bone marrow transplant

228
00:18:36,682 --> 00:18:38,149
have to be carried out immediately

229
00:18:38,450 --> 00:18:41,283
after the chemotherapy

230
00:18:46,358 --> 00:18:47,290
Otherwise, his life won't
last for more than 6 months.

231
00:18:47,593 --> 00:18:49,493
It is due to a number of
recent successful cases,

232
00:18:49,661 --> 00:18:50,719
being released afterwards.

233
00:18:51,330 --> 00:18:53,230
Everyone has some
understanding about it.

234
00:18:54,032 --> 00:18:55,260
Of course,

235
00:18:55,434 --> 00:18:57,925
it can't be cured completely.

236
00:18:58,804 --> 00:19:00,829
But, you should prepare it psychology.

