all the flights are maintaining the
normal schedules for the time being.

1065
01:11:31,320 --> 01:11:32,844
This is the report for the moment.

1066
01:11:33,689 --> 01:11:35,179
God, it's too bad!

1067
01:11:35,958 --> 01:11:36,788
What shall we do?

1068
01:11:37,526 --> 01:11:39,255
We ring up Bon and say
that we'll a bit late.

1069
01:11:39,928 --> 01:11:41,361
I've kept ringing him
but can't get through.

1070
01:11:56,478 --> 01:11:57,206
Excuse me.

1071
01:11:57,446 --> 01:11:58,470
Are there any flights to Hong Kong

1072
01:11:58,747 --> 01:11:59,679
after 5 pm?

1073
01:12:10,159 --> 01:12:12,684
Mum, I feel very painful.

1074
01:12:16,332 --> 01:12:17,663
Fai, be good.

1075
01:12:18,300 --> 01:12:20,860
Just give a bit more patient,
Uncle will soon be here.

1076
01:12:22,871 --> 01:12:23,895
Mum

1077
01:12:24,807 --> 01:12:26,604
I want to wear my new football T-shirt.

1078
01:12:30,979 --> 01:12:31,968
Let me think about it.

1079
01:12:48,364 --> 01:12:49,194
Please.

1080
01:12:49,631 --> 01:12:50,563
Alright.

1081
01:12:51,834 --> 01:12:53,324
Fai, do you know why Mum

1082
01:12:53,502 --> 01:12:54,696
bought you such large size?

1083
01:12:58,741 --> 01:13:00,174
It's because when you grow up,

1084
01:13:00,342 --> 01:13:01,707
you can still wear it.

1085
01:13:02,044 --> 01:13:03,636
So, you don't have to
ask me get you a new one.

1086
01:13:05,280 --> 01:13:07,544
Mum, you're so stingy.

1087
01:13:10,719 --> 01:13:13,882
Mum, can I wait till...

1088
01:13:14,256 --> 01:13:16,156
the day to put on this
new football T-shirt.

1089
01:13:20,362 --> 01:13:21,454
Of course.

1090
01:13:22,231 --> 01:13:22,788
On that day,

1091
01:13:22,965 --> 01:13:24,796
Mum and Grandpa will go
to see your match too.

1092
01:13:25,667 --> 01:13:28,135
Fai, you have to hold on to it.

1093
01:13:28,537 --> 01:13:31,131
Don't let your Mum down, okay?

1094
01:13:31,974 --> 01:13:32,998
Mum

1095
01:13:52,361 --> 01:13:54,659
Chi Yuen, we can't move as
it's block at the far end.

1096
01:13:55,264 --> 01:13:56,595
Would it be the earthquake
damaged the road?

1097
01:13:57,666 --> 01:13:58,325
I go and have a look.

1098
01:14:01,103 --> 01:14:01,865
How's it?

1099
01:14:02,604 --> 01:14:03,502
It looks like there was an accident.

1100
01:14:03,739 --> 01:14:04,330
Really?

1101
01:14:04,740 --> 01:14:05,468
Very serious.

1102
01:14:05,774 --> 01:14:06,741
Is there any other road?

1103
01:14:06,909 --> 01:14:07,534
I've a look.

1104
01:14:07,843 --> 01:14:08,741
Come back quickly!

1105
01:14:16,585 --> 01:14:17,609
I am a doctor, can I help?

1106
01:14:17,786 --> 01:14:18,616
Good, inside there...

1107
01:14:22,825 --> 01:14:24,087
Don't touch her...

1108
01:14:24,259 --> 01:14:25,419
I am a doctor, excuse me.

1109
01:14:34,736 --> 01:14:35,600
Her breath and pulse are stop.

1110
01:14:35,771 --> 01:14:37,329
Nurse...

1111
01:14:37,506 --> 01:14:39,406
This patient needed
emergency treatment, quickly!

1112
01:14:40,108 --> 01:14:40,972
Carry her out first!

1113
01:14:43,612 --> 01:14:44,909
Be careful, stretcher...

1114
01:14:45,948 --> 01:14:46,880
Stretcher...

1115
01:14:47,983 --> 01:14:49,575
Quick, help her for emergency treatment!

1116
01:15:00,496 --> 01:15:01,463
Don't move the patient.

1117
01:15:01,830 --> 01:15:03,821
His leg might have a fracture,
help him to fix it in position.

1118
01:15:06,001 --> 01:15:07,025
How's it? Can you move?

1119
01:15:13,442 --> 01:15:16,138
Telephone can't get through
because of the earthquake.

1120
01:15:18,914 --> 01:15:20,381
Are you alright? Where is the pain?

1121
01:15:21,416 --> 01:15:23,247
Leg... My leg hurts!

1122
01:15:24,887 --> 01:15:26,787
Hello, Bon.

1123
01:15:27,356 --> 01:15:29,017
I couldn't get through
your telephone at all.

1124
01:15:29,391 --> 01:15:30,688
My God, where are you?

1125
01:15:32,261 --> 01:15:33,250
Can you move?

1126
01:15:34,696 --> 01:15:36,095
I don't know where we are.

1127
01:15:36,798 --> 01:15:37,560
You don't know?

1128
01:15:38,333 --> 01:15:39,595
What do you mean by you don't know?

1129
01:15:39,768 --> 01:15:41,235
How can one don't know where one is?

1130
01:15:41,403 --> 01:15:43,394
No, there was a traffic
accident ahead of us.

1131
01:15:43,605 --> 01:15:44,629
Chi Yuen is helping to save people.

1132
01:15:48,243 --> 01:15:49,801
It should be alright, be careful.

1133
01:15:49,978 --> 01:15:51,172
My daughter? Where's my daughter?

1134
01:15:55,317 --> 01:15:55,874
Is she okay?

1135
01:15:56,051 --> 01:15:56,779
All yours.

1136
01:15:56,952 --> 01:15:57,748
Okay.

1137
01:15:59,354 --> 01:16:01,288
Dr Kao must have forgotten the time.

1138
01:16:01,924 --> 01:16:04,085
Ms Suen, do you mind to hurry up a bit?

1139
01:16:04,526 --> 01:16:06,221
If we can't catch the plane
at 5 p. M to Hong Kong,

1140
01:16:06,528 --> 01:16:07,961
then we certainly can't
catch the one at 7:50 p. m.

1141
01:16:08,130 --> 01:16:09,859
The last flight from
Hong Kong to Beijing.

1142
01:16:10,032 --> 01:16:11,124
Then, we're screwed!

1143
01:16:11,366 --> 01:16:12,526
I know! I know!

1144
01:16:13,101 --> 01:16:13,829
Okay, bye!

1145
01:16:24,680 --> 01:16:25,476
Chi Yuen!

1146
01:16:26,848 --> 01:16:27,678
Chi Yuen!

1147
01:16:29,918 --> 01:16:30,907
Chi Yuen, alright?

1148
01:16:31,286 --> 01:16:32,344
You get on first...

1149
01:16:32,788 --> 01:16:33,755
I've already contacted with Bon.

1150
01:16:33,989 --> 01:16:34,478
He said that

1151
01:16:34,656 --> 01:16:36,556
if we couldn't make it in
30 minutes to the airport,

1152
01:16:36,725 --> 01:16:39,751
we won't be able to catch the
last flight to Beijing at 7:50 p. m.

1153
01:16:39,928 --> 01:16:40,417
Excuse me.

1154
01:16:40,629 --> 01:16:41,653
Are you listening?

1155
01:16:41,897 --> 01:16:43,489
No problem, go round the lanes.

1156
01:16:47,102 --> 01:16:48,000
Was that man okay?

1157
01:16:48,604 --> 01:16:49,434
He hurt his chest.

1158
01:16:49,771 --> 01:16:50,999
Life should be no danger.

1159
01:16:52,407 --> 01:16:53,567
You really want to go with the driver?

1160
01:16:54,209 --> 01:16:55,335
If we made a mistake, it'll be finished.

1161
01:16:56,378 --> 01:16:57,640
The driver should know
the routes very well.

1162
01:16:58,146 --> 01:16:59,943
Also, we have no other choice.

1163
01:17:00,582 --> 01:17:01,549
Time is running out.

1164
01:17:07,589 --> 01:17:08,112
What is the matter?

1165
01:17:08,390 --> 01:17:09,516
Which is the right route to the airport?

1166
01:17:09,691 --> 01:17:11,283
Listen to me, I'm so sure.

1167
01:17:11,460 --> 01:17:12,893
I go the airport everyday.

1168
01:17:13,161 --> 01:17:14,856
There's a chimney in
the front, can't you see?

1169
01:17:15,097 --> 01:17:16,064
Then, turn right.

1170
01:17:16,231 --> 01:17:17,391
Thank you! Thank you!

1171
01:17:17,899 --> 01:17:19,696
The earthquake has
just over, be careful!

1172
01:17:34,216 --> 01:17:35,205
Watch out!

1173
01:17:36,652 --> 01:17:37,311
Oh no!

1174
01:17:38,220 --> 01:17:38,914
I'll go and shove it.

1175
01:17:41,189 --> 01:17:43,180
Give way Brother Cow!

1176
01:17:43,592 --> 01:17:45,924
We're in a hurry, don't come over...

1177
01:17:46,228 --> 01:17:47,695
Go over there, quick...

1178
01:17:48,163 --> 01:17:49,289
That's it. Don't come out.

1179
01:17:55,704 --> 01:17:56,762
Its head is blocking the way.

1180
01:17:56,938 --> 01:17:58,929
No problem, I'll watch out.

1181
01:18:00,575 --> 01:18:01,473
Go away, go away.

1182
01:18:02,611 --> 01:18:03,509
Don't come over here.

1183
01:18:29,871 --> 01:18:31,202
Are you sure this is correct?

1184
01:18:31,673 --> 01:18:32,469
Should be correct.

1185
01:18:32,974 --> 01:18:33,668
But, I think...

1186
01:18:33,842 --> 01:18:35,867
I think there's no roads in the front.

1187
01:18:36,511 --> 01:18:38,445
This is a property road and it
should be connecting to outside.

1188
01:18:39,414 --> 01:18:40,438
How soon shall we arrive?

1189
01:18:41,016 --> 01:18:42,415
It's only 15 minutes left.

1190
01:18:44,820 --> 01:18:45,752
We may not be able to make it.

1191
01:18:55,363 --> 01:18:56,159
Sit still!

1192
01:18:59,968 --> 01:19:01,731
There's no road...

1193
01:19:09,244 --> 01:19:10,302
The bridge is broken, what shall we do?

1194
01:19:11,513 --> 01:19:12,480
Drive over it, be careful!

1195
01:19:27,395 --> 01:19:28,453
Be careful!

1196
01:19:45,981 --> 01:19:47,005
My hand seems to be dislocated.

1197
01:19:52,254 --> 01:19:54,484
Incredible... the bend
starts with the slant.

1198
01:19:54,723 --> 01:19:55,348
Yan Yan!

1199
01:19:55,791 --> 01:19:57,281
I can't open the door!

1200
01:19:57,993 --> 01:19:59,324
You try my side.

1201
01:20:03,365 --> 01:20:04,195
You okay?

1202
01:20:05,967 --> 01:20:08,060
Bone marrow... One pack is missing!

1203
01:20:09,204 --> 01:20:09,932
How come it's missing?

1204
01:20:10,305 --> 01:20:10,862
I don't know.

1205
01:20:17,345 --> 01:20:21,475
Finished... what can we do?

1206
01:20:22,184 --> 01:20:23,242
It's over there!

1207
01:20:37,265 --> 01:20:38,732
Driver, do you mind to go a bit fast!

1208
01:20:39,067 --> 01:20:40,500
Thanks for your help. We're in a hurry.

1209
01:20:42,404 --> 01:20:44,372
TAIPEI CKS INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT

1210
01:20:45,340 --> 01:20:46,136
Bon, quick!

1211
01:20:47,175 --> 01:20:47,971
Quick!

1212
01:20:48,610 --> 01:20:49,736
What happened to you?

1213
01:20:50,312 --> 01:20:51,745
Let's go inside first.
Can we still make it?

1214
01:20:52,013 --> 01:20:53,947
There's a flight to Hong
Kong in 40 minutes later.

1215
01:20:54,182 --> 01:20:55,945
The last flight from Hong
Kong to Beijing is impossible.

1216
01:20:56,284 --> 01:20:57,945
Impossible! What shall be do?

1217
01:20:58,220 --> 01:21:00,051
Don't panic. I've already
contacted with the Airline.

1218
01:21:00,388 --> 01:21:01,320
There's still no news at the moment.

1219
01:21:01,857 --> 01:21:02,881
You'd better go and check.

1220
01:21:03,458 --> 01:21:05,255
Okay. You wait and I go and ask again.

1221
01:21:14,469 --> 01:21:15,697
Ms... Excuse me.

1222
01:21:15,937 --> 01:21:17,996
I've just explained to you
regarding that thing, how's it now?

1223
01:21:33,188 --> 01:21:34,086
It's my fault.

1224
01:21:35,223 --> 01:21:37,282
I only thought of the emergency
work and forgot the time.

1225
01:21:38,627 --> 01:21:39,491
This ended up of this delay.

1226
01:21:40,428 --> 01:21:43,158
If we couldn't catch the flight,
what would happen to Luk Fai?

1227
01:21:45,166 --> 01:21:46,360
You shouldn't blame yourself.

1228
01:21:47,302 --> 01:21:48,769
Under such situation,

1229
01:21:49,037 --> 01:21:50,698
no one will turn a blind eye
and do nothing to save life.

1230
01:21:54,175 --> 01:21:55,802
Also, there's still a chance.

1231
01:21:56,478 --> 01:21:57,911
Aren't we still waiting for the news?

1232
01:22:00,615 --> 01:22:01,547
Is your hand alright?

1233
01:22:17,933 --> 01:22:21,391
The Dragon Air in H.K. Have
already known about the delivery

1234
01:22:21,636 --> 01:22:22,034
of your bone marrow
business There's no problem.

1235
01:22:22,203 --> 01:22:22,567
Okay?

1236
01:22:22,737 --> 01:22:23,567
Okay.

1237
01:22:23,738 --> 01:22:24,796
Thank you...

1238
01:22:25,340 --> 01:22:25,965
Thank you!

1239
01:22:27,309 --> 01:22:28,640
Quick... Get ready for boarding!

1240
01:22:29,344 --> 01:22:31,312
The airline has already
contacted the H.K. Airport.

1241
01:22:31,479 --> 01:22:32,036
They said

1242
01:22:32,213 --> 01:22:34,238
the last flight of Dragon Air
is willing to wait for you.

1243
01:22:34,416 --> 01:22:35,508
Really? It's great!

1244
01:22:39,187 --> 01:22:39,915
What's it?

1245
01:22:44,759 --> 01:22:47,091
It hurts very much...

1246
01:22:53,535 --> 01:22:55,162
It hurts very much!

1247
01:22:58,306 --> 01:22:59,102
What are you doing?

1248
01:23:03,144 --> 01:23:05,510
You want me to go on board like this?

1249
01:23:14,556 --> 01:23:15,215
This is...

1250
01:23:15,390 --> 01:23:16,448
already 20 pieces of tie.

1251
01:23:21,262 --> 01:23:22,320
Really?

1252
01:23:34,609 --> 01:23:36,201
You can't deny.

1253
01:24:25,060 --> 01:24:26,618
ONE YEAR LATER

1254
01:24:27,062 --> 01:24:29,121
LUK FAI'S HOUSE, BEIJING

1255
01:25:15,944 --> 01:25:18,310
Madam Chan... Grandpa's
finger is moving!

1256
01:25:19,013 --> 01:25:20,310
Great!

1257
01:25:21,049 --> 01:25:23,040
His thumb is really can hold up!

1258
01:25:35,230 --> 01:25:37,289
Luk Fai, Congratulations!

1259
01:25:38,600 --> 01:25:39,726
Thank you!

1260
01:25:40,135 --> 01:25:40,999
Congratulations! Luk Fai.

1261
01:25:42,337 --> 01:25:43,429
Do you know who is this gentleman?

1262
01:25:46,407 --> 01:25:48,341
He's the person who has
donated his bone marrow to you.

1263
01:25:57,785 --> 01:25:58,911
Uncle!

1264
01:26:34,989 --> 01:26:46,230
All bone marrow donations would not
do any harm to the person at all.

